text: Olivia "Polly" Holohan (born 4 July 1959) is an Irish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Irish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
